Nigerian singer, David Adeleke, popularly known as Davido, has revealed how the Nigerian musician, Augustine Miles Kelechi aka Tekno helped his career by bringing him back to the limelight. Davido revealed this while speaking tomedia personality, Ebuka Obi-Uchendu on the Bounce Radio programme The Omo Baba Olowi crooner said, “Till date, I am still grateful to Tekno. Tekno brought me back, I didn’t have a hit for almost a year. “Tekno wrote the song, “IF” and he wanted me to record the song. He wanted me to do it because I am a good guy”.